ZIO Blocks Chunk Contribution
I've created the new standalone zio.blocks.chunk project as a top-level directory in the repository. This is a pure, effect-free replication of ZIO's Chunk data structure, optimized for performance with balanced concatenation using a tree structure inspired by Conc-Trees. All effectful methods (e.g., mapZIO, collectZIO, foreach, etc.) have been omitted. The implementation is contained in a single Chunk.scala file.
