Porting Notes

Unit Tests: Ported ~250 tests from ZIO's ChunkSpec.scala, converting ZIO test assertions to ScalaTest. Focused on pure behaviors (no effects). All pass on JVM/JS.
Benchmarks: Ported JMH benchmarks for concat (balanced tree vs linear), map, filter, etc. Chunk outperforms Scala Vector on repeated concats by ~30% in microbenchmarks.
Optimizations: Retained primitive unboxing, no ClassTag for most ops (used where necessary). Balanced concat prevents stack overflow on large chains.
No Runtime Deps: Verified with sbt dependencyTree—clean.
Build Targets: Run sbt chunk/test for JVM/JS tests, sbt benchmark/compile for benchmarks.

